query:
SELECT id, nome, pesquisaId, projectId, createdAt 
FROM clientes 
WHERE LOWER(nome) LIKE '%veol%' OR LOWER(nome) LIKE '%veo%'
ORDER BY createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 10;
